00:00:08.892 --> 00:00:11.740 align:middle line:84%
>> CHARLES SHULTS: It's going
to pervade our lives at every

00:00:11.740 --> 00:00:12.795 align:middle line:90%
level very soon.

00:00:12.795 --> 00:00:14.920 align:middle line:84%
So it's good to know where
we stand, what it means,

00:00:14.920 --> 00:00:15.920 align:middle line:90%
and what it's all about.

00:00:15.920 --> 00:00:17.650 align:middle line:84%
All of this is an
exploration to see

00:00:17.650 --> 00:00:19.940 align:middle line:84%
how we can open up
the brain without,

00:00:19.940 --> 00:00:21.850 align:middle line:84%
of course, destroying
the autonomy

00:00:21.850 --> 00:00:22.990 align:middle line:90%
of the individual person.

00:00:22.990 --> 00:00:24.910 align:middle line:84%
The big question is,
if it's smart enough

00:00:24.910 --> 00:00:27.250 align:middle line:84%
to understand what you're
instructing it to do,

00:00:27.250 --> 00:00:30.100 align:middle line:84%
why would it want to do
what you tell it and not

00:00:30.100 --> 00:00:31.460 align:middle line:90%
what it wants to do?

00:00:31.460 --> 00:00:34.060 align:middle line:84%
We're going to be merged with
machinery the way things are

00:00:34.060 --> 00:00:36.610 align:middle line:84%
going, and perhaps that
might be the solution

00:00:36.610 --> 00:00:40.630 align:middle line:84%
to an impending machine disaster
that people imagine coming.

00:00:40.630 --> 00:00:43.060 align:middle line:90%
What makes you you?

00:00:43.060 --> 00:00:45.777 align:middle line:84%
Life itself is natural
nanotechnology.

00:00:45.777 --> 00:00:47.860 align:middle line:84%
>> REGINA MEREDITH: Explain
what you mean by that.

00:00:47.860 --> 00:00:51.560 align:middle line:90%


00:00:51.560 --> 00:00:53.630 align:middle line:10%
