Charles Shults,

00:00:53.630 --> 00:00:56.300 align:middle line:10%
has worked on weapons
systems, missile systems,

00:00:56.300 --> 00:00:59.240 align:middle line:10%
and advanced attack helicopter
systems for the aerospace

00:00:59.240 --> 00:01:00.090 align:middle line:10%
industry.

00:01:00.090 --> 00:01:03.170 align:middle line:84%
All of this led him to work
into the area of robotics

00:01:03.170 --> 00:01:05.420 align:middle line:84%
and AI for which he
attained knighthood.

00:01:05.420 --> 00:01:09.050 align:middle line:84%
He is here to have a very
direct conversation about AI

00:01:09.050 --> 00:01:10.760 align:middle line:84%
and how the citizens
of Earth will

00:01:10.760 --> 00:01:12.200 align:middle line:90%
be confronted with its use.

00:01:12.200 --> 00:01:14.840 align:middle line:84%
Good or bad, we're going
to take a nice look at it.

00:01:14.840 --> 00:01:16.555 align:middle line:90%
Charles, welcome to Open Minds.

00:01:16.555 --> 00:01:17.430 align:middle line:90%
>> Shults: Thank you.

00:01:17.430 --> 00:01:17.870 align:middle line:90%
It's a pleasure to be here.

00:01:17.870 --> 00:01:18.995 align:middle line:90%
>> REGINA: This should be--

00:01:18.995 --> 00:01:20.820 align:middle line:84%
you're so articulate
and well versed.

00:01:20.820 --> 00:01:22.820 align:middle line:84%
This should be a really
fascinating conversation

00:01:22.820 --> 00:01:26.150 align:middle line:84%
because it's scary for
people to contemplate.

00:01:26.150 --> 00:01:28.520 align:middle line:84%
If you're under
20, it's exciting.

00:01:28.520 --> 00:01:30.990 align:middle line:84%
If you're over 20, you
have some questions.

00:01:30.990 --> 00:01:31.790 align:middle line:90%
There's very--

