00:17:33.630 --> 00:17:35.640 align:middle line:90%
This is a very tricky question.

00:17:35.640 --> 00:17:36.640 align:middle line:90%
>> REGINA: It is tricky.

00:17:36.640 --> 00:17:39.100 align:middle line:84%
