00:17:47.550 --> 00:17:48.350 align:middle line:90%
>> REGINA: Yeah.

00:17:48.350 --> 00:17:51.690 align:middle line:84%
>> Shults: You don't want to
alter the normal development

00:17:51.690 --> 00:17:55.268 align:middle line:84%
