in a person or personality

00:17:55.268 --> 00:17:57.810 align:middle line:84%
that's entirely different from
what was originally happening.

00:17:57.810 --> 00:18:00.060 align:middle line:84%
>> REGINA: I
couldn't agree more.

00:18:00.060 --> 00:18:02.040 align:middle line:84%
So here you have
that, and then you

00:18:02.040 --> 00:18:04.620 align:middle line:84%
have Musk saying, this
is another use of it,

00:18:04.620 --> 00:18:06.120 align:middle line:90%
nothing to do with the human.

00:18:06.120 --> 00:18:10.680 align:middle line:84%
Now we're talking flat
out technological AI.

00:18:10.680 --> 00:18:14.130 align:middle line:84%
And he's oftentimes off in
his projections of time,

00:18:14.130 --> 00:18:16.750 align:middle line:84%
