getting into the subject

00:18:57.690 --> 00:19:01.170 align:middle line:84%
we're talking about, what
happens, A, when you introduce

00:19:01.170 --> 00:19:03.570 align:middle line:84%
these robots that
are better than us,

00:19:03.570 --> 00:19:08.130 align:middle line:84%
more caring, stronger,
smarter into our lives?

00:19:08.130 --> 00:19:10.860 align:middle line:84%
And what happens, if then
