00:22:51.440 --> 00:22:53.292 align:middle line:84%
which is putting a disk
basically right here

00:22:53.292 --> 00:22:54.125 align:middle line:90%
in the skull, right?

00:22:54.125 --> 00:22:54.925 align:middle line:90%
>> Shults: Correct.

00:22:54.925 --> 00:22:56.947 align:middle line:84%
>> REGINA: And now,
