and found a way to
communicate, but her mind

00:25:15.830 --> 00:25:18.080 align:middle line:90%
was perfectly intact.

00:25:18.080 --> 00:25:22.430 align:middle line:84%
And I think she did end her life
with assisted suicide, legal.

00:25:22.430 --> 00:25:25.070 align:middle line:84%
And I think what
would have happened

00:25:25.070 --> 00:25:26.450 align:middle line:90%
had that been available?

00:25:26.450 --> 00:25:27.620 align:middle line:90%
>> Shults: Right.

00:25:27.620 --> 00:25:31.820 align:middle line:84%
Well, obviously, restoring
the ability to communicate

00:25:31.820 --> 00:25:33.390 align:middle line:90%
is wonderful.

00:25:33.390 --> 00:25:35.720 align:middle line:84%
But if you can't stop
the damage, what's

00:25:35.720 --> 00:25:37.580 align:middle line:84%
causing the damage,
it may spread

00:25:37.580 --> 00:25:39.450 align:middle line:90%
to other areas of the brain.

00:25:39.450 --> 00:25:43.160 align:middle line:84%
So it sounds like a panacea,
just put this thing in.

00:25:43.160 --> 00:25:45.840 align:middle line:84%
But if the rest of the brain
is still failing rapidly,

00:25:45.840 --> 00:25:47.120 align:middle line:90%
it's a problem.

